## Implementation Plan

### Step 1: Create the minimal Jinja template for Mistral Instruct v0.3

**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775465726212-eiywt8/models/templates/mistralai-Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3.jinja`

